Introduction

New:ID is an upcoming all-Filipino boy group composed of members L, Jom, Macky, Thad, and Wilson. The group consists of former contestants from the reality survival show Dream Maker.

Despite not securing a spot in the group HORI7ON, the members caught the attention of MLD Entertainment and signed on as trainees on April 28, 2023.
